name: Ben Quadinaros' Podracer
Lore: 'Balta-Trabaat BT310 Podracer that utilizes four engines instead of two. Has the potential to be the fastest Podracer on the track, despite its inconsistent performance.',
Text: 'Deploy on Podrace Arena. Adds 1 to each of your race destinies here. Once during each of your control phases may lose 2 Force to exchange the topmost race destiny here with topmost race destiny of another Podracer.',
